scalePower(double) - Method in class org.firstinspires.ftc.team9202hme.math.PowerScale
Scales the input power based on the function y = (u - l) (x^(su)^x) + l, where y is the output power, x is the input power, u is the max power, l is the minimum power, and s is the scale interval.
